<blockquote>
    <h1><font color="#FF0000" face="Arial,Helvetica">Project to
    Intercompare Regional Climate Simulations (PIRCS) </font></h1>
    <table border="0" cellpadding="16">
        <tr>
            <td><img src="smpircslogo.gif" align="left"
            hspace="0" width="108" height="150" valign="CENTER"> </td>
            <td><font size="+1"><i>The mission of PIRCS is to provide a common
            framework for evaluating strengths and weaknesses
            of regional climate models and their component
            procedures through systematic, comparative
            simulations.</i> </font></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
